::Hevngjerrig::
       "Hmm?  What was that?  Asking after a lost love?"  He shakes his head 
bemused.  "No, I assure you I am not him, whomever he may be."  He feigns 
ignorance quite certain she mouthed the name of Hydras.  "I am known as 
Hevngjerrig.  That is all that I am."
